<div class="com-share" data-id="3256" data-title="《没错！年轻人还是爱看电影哒！》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/3256/medium/3256.jpg?1436637531" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/3256" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
